0.60 oz Amarillo [9.30 %] - Boil 60.0 min Hop 3 24.3 IBUs
0.25 oz Amarillo [9.30 %] - Boil 20.0 min Hop 4 6.1 IBUs

1.00 Items Whirlfloc Tablet (Boil 15.0 mins) Fining 5 -

1.0 pkg Cream Ale Yeast Blend (White Labs #WLP080) [50.28 ml] Yeast 6 â€“



 		  <%= label_tag "org_gravity", caption: "Original Gravity" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "org_gravity", id: "org_gravity",
            value: @recipe.org_gravity %>

      <%= label_tag "org_gravity_temp", caption: "Temp" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "org_gravity_temp", id: "org_gravity_temp",
            value: @recipe.org_gravity_temp %>

      <%= label_tag "final_gravity", caption: "Final Gravity" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "final_gravity", id: "final_gravity",
            value: @recipe.final_gravity %>

      <%= label_tag "final_gravity_temp", caption: "Temp" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "final_gravity_temp", id: "final_gravity_temp",
            value: @recipe.final_gravity_temp %>

      <%= label_tag "ibu", caption: "IBU" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "ibu", id: "ibu",
            value: @recipe.ibu %>

            
            


      <%= label_tag "boil_time", caption: "Boil Time (minutes)" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "boil_time", id: "boil_time",
            value: @recipe.boil_time %>

      <%= label_tag "boil_time", caption: "Boil Time (minutes)" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "boil_time", id: "boil_time",
            value: @recipe.boil_time %>

      <%= label_tag "color", caption: "Beer Color" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "color", id: "color",
            value: @recipe.color %>


      <%= label_tag "pri_ferm_days", caption: "Primary Fermentation (# of days & temp)" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "pri_ferm_days", id: "pri_ferm_days",
            value: @recipe.pri_ferm_days %>
      <%= label_tag "pri_ferm_temp" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "pri_ferm_temp", id: "pri_ferm_temp",
            value: @recipe.pri_ferm_temp %>

      <%= label_tag "pri_ferm_notes", caption: "Primary Fermentation Notes" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "pri_ferm_notes", id: "pri_ferm_notes",
            value: @recipe.pri_ferm_notes %>

      <%= label_tag "sec_ferm_days", caption: "Secondary Fermentation (# of days & temp" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "sec_ferm_days", id: "sec_ferm_days",
            value: @recipe.sec_ferm_days %>
      <%= label_tag "sec_ferm_temp" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "sec_ferm_temp", id: "sec_ferm_temp",
            value: @recipe.sec_ferm_temp %>
         
      <%= label_tag "sec_ferm_notes", caption: "Secondary Fermentation Notes" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "sec_ferm_notes", id: "sec_ferm_notes",
            value: @recipe.sec_ferm_notes %>  



      <%= label_tag "taste_rating", caption: "Taste Rating" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "taste_rating", id: "taste_rating",
            value: @recipe.taste_rating %>
            
      <%= label_tag "tasting_notes", caption: "Tasting Notes" %>
      <%= text_field_tag "tasting_notes", id: "tasting_notes",
            value: @recipe.tasting_notes %>




Actual Alcohol by Vol:
Bitterness:
Calories (per 12oz):
Est Color: 4.5 SRM



      <br>
      <div class='label-spacer'></div>
      <button name="action" value="save">Save</button>
      <br>
    <% end %>
  </body>

</html>
